                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">添加以下参数：</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:blue">&lt;property </span><span style="color:red">name</span><span
                style="color:blue">=</span><span style="color:#a31515">"url" </span><span
                style="color:red">value</span><span style="color:blue">=</span><span
                style="color:#a31515">"jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/mydata?useUnicode=true</span><span
                style="color:#00b0e8">&amp;amp;</span><span style="color:#a31515">characterEncoding=utf-8</span><span
                style="color:#00b0e8">&amp;amp;</span><span style="color:#a31515">serverTimezone=GMT"</span><span
                style="color:blue"> /&gt;</span></span></span></p>
